data.description: Come see this charming one owner home in the popular River Oaks subdivision. Columns on the front porch definitely add character to this one. The home has a great split floor plan for families wanting a little privacy. High ceilings in the living room and bedrooms make this home feel open and spacious. Wood burning fireplace for those cool winter evenings. Plantation shutters throughout bringing lots of character to the home. Double vanities in the master and a garden tub for relaxing after those long days at work. Kitchen has beautiful oak cabinets, a nice sized pantry and granite countertops. Outside you have a nice tiled, covered patio for entertaining and a wired workshop for those must do projects.Very lovely home loooking for someone to come love it!
